<body>
<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="957300000t" end="981600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">结果你成为军人了吗</p>
<p begin="994400000t" end="1036300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">果然传授你焰之炼金术还为时过早</p>
<p begin="1041500000t" end="1058600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">为时…过早？</p>
<p begin="1065700000t" end="1077200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">结果直到最后</p>
<p begin="1082400000t" end="1111800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">您还是只教了我炼金术的基础而已</p>
<p begin="1117900000t" end="1128600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">当然</p>
<p begin="1135400000t" end="1160600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">会成为军队走狗的家伙</p>
<p begin="1162200000t" end="1193900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">光是教些基础已经过于浪费</p>
<p begin="1216700000t" end="1248900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">您的意思是炼金术应该为大众服务吗</p>
<p begin="1273800000t" end="1315700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">老师 现在周边诸国的威胁已经迫在眉睫</p>
<p begin="1318600000t" end="1338600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">强化军队才是当务之急</p>
<p begin="1342900000t" end="1367000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">为了保护国民 炼金术是…</p>
<p begin="1367500000t" end="1387100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">这种借口我已经听烦了</p>
<p begin="1458400000t" end="1478200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">我无法忍受</p>
<p begin="1484200000t" end="1523000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">为何像您这样的人要过着这种贫寒的生活</p>
<p begin="1531700000t" end="1547800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">去取得国家资格吧</p>
<p begin="1552300000t" end="1568200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">这样的话就能进行更深入的研究…</p>
<p begin="1568700000t" end="1598100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">研究早在很久以前就已经完成了</p>
<p begin="1608700000t" end="1619900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">您说什么？</p>
<p begin="1630300000t" end="1656200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">它是最高最强的炼金术</p>
<p begin="1660400000t" end="1692000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">但是随着使用方法的不同也能变成灾厄</p>
<p begin="1698600000t" end="1750800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">我完成了它 然后就此满足了</p>
<p begin="1780700000t" end="1804700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">炼金术师是一种只要还活着</p>
<p begin="1806700000t" end="1837900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">就会不断追求真理的生物</p>
<p begin="1845500000t" end="1885100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">放弃思考也就意味着炼金术师的死亡</p>
<p begin="1893500000t" end="1922800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">我早在很久以前就已经死…</p>
<p begin="1934600000t" end="1942900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">老师！</p>
<p begin="1977500000t" end="1997000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">老师！霍克艾老师！</p>
<p begin="2005100000t" end="2028500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">女儿就拜托了…</p>
<p begin="2036000000t" end="2053100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">我的研究…</p>
<p begin="2056800000t" end="2088200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">全部…由我女儿…</p>
<p begin="2187100000t" end="2225300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">抱歉 从头到尾都劳烦您帮忙</p>
<p begin="2229900000t" end="2261800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">不必在意 这是弟子应该做的</p>
<p begin="2275700000t" end="2309600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">发生什么事的话 可以随时来军部找我</p>
<p begin="2345100000t" end="2382200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">你也会看不起我成为军人的事吗</p>
<p begin="2388200000t" end="2427500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">的确 我随时有可能成为路边的一只死狗</p>
<p begin="2433600000t" end="2442700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">但即便如此</p>
<p begin="2446900000t" end="2469100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我还是认为只要能成为这个国家的基石</p>
<p begin="2473400000t" end="2509400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">以此来守护他人 这对我来说就是一种幸福</p>
<p begin="2524000000t" end="2553700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">哎呀…我说的这种梦想很幼稚吧</p>
<p begin="2565400000t" end="2598500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">不 我觉得这是很伟大的梦想</p>
<p begin="2618100000t" end="2641000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">所有人都能幸福生活的未来…</p>
<p begin="2647600000t" end="2661000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">我可以相信您吗</p>
<p begin="2677800000t" end="2713100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">能将父亲的梦想托付给您吗</p>
<p begin="2836600000t" end="2854500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">疾风号 不行</p>
<p begin="2872200000t" end="2884000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">抱歉了</p>
<p begin="2886300000t" end="2907900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">没啥 常有的事了</p>
<p begin="2921900000t" end="2951000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">我听说了 是总统辅佐官？</p>
<p begin="2960000000t" end="2968800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">嗯</p>
<p begin="3005400000t" end="3025500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">看起来相当艰难呢</p>
<p begin="3031600000t" end="3046600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">没有杀人</p>
<p begin="3054800000t" end="3068500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">最后没有杀人就解决了</p>
<p begin="3107400000t" end="3133500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">不 是下不了手</p>
<p begin="3156200000t" end="3170600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">这样不行吧</p>
<p begin="3174900000t" end="3203800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">觉悟不够就只是拖别人的后腿</p>
<p begin="3221800000t" end="3234600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">发生什么了吗</p>
<p begin="3252500000t" end="3291900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">斯卡是杀了温莉父母的仇人</p>
<p begin="3316200000t" end="3357300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">那个时候从心底里感到厌恶</p>
<p begin="3366000000t" end="3392400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">然后突然就觉得枪是很可怕的东西</p>
<p begin="3400200000t" end="3413500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">等回过神来…</p>
<p begin="3436100000t" end="3481000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">她恨斯卡恨到要亲手杀了他</p>
<p begin="3487600000t" end="3517000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">但马上又嚎啕大哭</p>
<p begin="3536500000t" end="3550100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">真是不行啊</p>
<p begin="3556000000t" end="3588000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">我一点都不了解她</p>
<p begin="3594900000t" end="3623400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">这是只有活下来的人才会有的烦恼</p>
<p begin="3640700000t" end="3656700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">但是你必须活下去</p>
<p begin="3665000000t" end="3681800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">哪怕只是为了重要的人也好</p>
<p begin="3697700000t" end="3710000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">要保护好她哦</p>
<p begin="3722600000t" end="3750600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">你很喜欢温莉的吧</p>
<p begin="3781100000t" end="3799700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">不…不对啦！</p>
<p begin="3800500000t" end="3821000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">她…她只是单纯的青梅竹马而已</p>
<p begin="3821900000t" end="3834900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">就…就好像我的家人一样</p>
<p begin="3836000000t" end="3849300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">说什么守护不守护的</p>
<p begin="3850400000t" end="3867100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">那根本理所当然嘛 那个…</p>
<p begin="3867700000t" end="3879300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">对不起</p>
<p begin="3887100000t" end="3914200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">这给你带来了很沉重的负担吧</p>
<p begin="3973000000t" end="4008600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">中尉 你不会觉得很沉重吗</p>
<p begin="4017200000t" end="4035000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">不管轻还是重</p>
<p begin="4040900000t" end="4068300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">我现在都没有评价的资格了</p>
<p begin="4083200000t" end="4111200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">因为我在过去夺去了许多人的生命</p>
<p begin="4119000000t" end="4163800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">而且 走上这条道路也是我自己的选择</p>
<p begin="4183200000t" end="4194500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">伊修瓦尔？</p>
<p begin="4218200000t" end="4252300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">能不能说说伊修瓦尔的事情？</p>
<p begin="4299000000t" end="4313400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">从实招来吧</p>
<p begin="4319800000t" end="4352900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">在伊修瓦尔你们到底都干了些什么</p>
<p begin="4372300000t" end="4410500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">伊修瓦尔是块遍布岩石沙砾 不利人类生存的土地</p>
<p begin="4415900000t" end="4429000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">也正因为是这样的大地</p>
<p begin="4430900000t" end="4451200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">孕育出戒律森严的宗教</p>
<p begin="4452900000t" end="4491800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">与坚韧的民族可谓是理所当然</p>
<p begin="4499300000t" end="4508200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">但是</p>
<p begin="4510800000t" end="4534000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">因为与亚美斯特利斯的合并</p>
<p begin="4538100000t" end="4566600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">招来了一部分人不满</p>
<p begin="4576500000t" end="4588700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">就在这时…</p>
<p begin="4641900000t" end="4658500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">因为一颗子弹</p>
<p begin="4660400000t" end="4698900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">不满变成了愤怒 最终波及到伊修瓦尔全境</p>
<p begin="4746600000t" end="4797300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">暴动最后演变成内乱 持续了整整七年</p>
<p begin="4826300000t" end="4863200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">最后一张文件决定了一切</p>
<p begin="4875100000t" end="4899100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">总统令3066号</p>
<p begin="4905300000t" end="4935200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">宣告了伊修瓦尔歼灭战开始的</p>
<p begin="4940300000t" end="4954300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">就是这么一张纸片</p>
<p begin="5127200000t" end="5145300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">那是名副其实的地狱</p>
<p begin="5162200000t" end="5189600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">空气中充满了腐臭与硝烟</p>
<p begin="5195490000t" end="5222400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">沙砾中浸染着流下的鲜血</p>
<p begin="5288900000t" end="5316600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">普通的士兵只是胡乱开枪</p>
<p begin="5318300000t" end="5350500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">偶尔其中一发子弹会夺去别人性命</p>
<p begin="5359000000t" end="5375000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">但是狙击就不同</p>
<p begin="5380300000t" end="5408600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">每次扣下扳机 必然会有人死去</p>
<p begin="5419000000t" end="5458400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">能将原因与结果如此明显相连的</p>
<p begin="5461500000t" end="5473900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">就只有狙击兵…</p>
<p begin="5489800000t" end="5511500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">以及国家炼金术师而已了</p>
<p begin="5535900000t" end="5583800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">吾名为铁血之炼金术师 巴斯克·格兰</p>
<p begin="5593000000t" end="5628600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">铁与血 即是兵器与士兵</p>
<p begin="5631100000t" end="5677100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">此身将成为战斗之先驱立下战功！</p>
<p begin="6057100000t" end="6090400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">混蛋 伊修瓦尔的死小鬼！</p>
<p begin="6093000000t" end="6121300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">居然敢…天杀的！</p>
<p begin="6148300000t" end="6171700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">罗伊！罗伊·玛斯坦！</p>
<p begin="6210900000t" end="6242600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">你也来了啊 真是久违了</p>
<p begin="6247000000t" end="6281600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">不过 你的眼神变了啊</p>
<p begin="6310700000t" end="6348300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">你也一样 那是杀人者的眼神</p>
<p begin="6360500000t" end="6368500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">是呢</p>
<p begin="6391000000t" end="6404700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">在士官学校的时候</p>
<p begin="6407300000t" end="6445500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">大家还一起讨论过这个国家的未来呢</p>
<p begin="6447000000t" end="6482200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">是啊 那真是一个美好的未来</p>
<p begin="6488700000t" end="6506300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">上尉 您的信件</p>
<p begin="6509700000t" end="6527100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">好 谢谢你了</p>
<p begin="6551000000t" end="6564200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">怎…怎么了？</p>
<p begin="6566000000t" end="6605700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">我的美好未来啊！她叫格蕾希娅</p>
<p begin="6606700000t" end="6643000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">一直在中央市等着我回去呢！</p>
<p begin="6652800000t" end="6665900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">孤独地等…</p>
<p begin="6682400000t" end="6711300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">被其他男人横刀夺爱该怎么办！</p>
<p begin="6712100000t" end="6758100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">不 格蕾希娅不会放着我这种好男人去花心的</p>
<p begin="6758500000t" end="6772900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">不过…</p>
<p begin="6773500000t" end="6801200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">修兹 我先给你一个忠告</p>
<p begin="6805200000t" end="6829800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">这是电影和小说里经常有的桥段</p>
<p begin="6836100000t" end="6874100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">在战场上谈起恋人的家伙 死得都很快</p>
<p begin="6882300000t" end="6896000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">我说你啊…</p>
<p begin="6937300000t" end="6963700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">这样我起码能活到明天</p>
<p begin="6977900000t" end="7018900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">这封信能让我梦到明天</p>
<p begin="7028000000t" end="7055700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">在不知何时才会结束的这个战场上…</p>
<p begin="7069800000t" end="7093600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">真是看不到出口的战争啊</p>
<p begin="7100000000t" end="7126900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">不管国家投入多少兵力</p>
<p begin="7132800000t" end="7158900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">这个沙漠也会如同吸水一样全部吸收</p>
<p begin="7171400000t" end="7204100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">下力气去进行镇压 最后又能留下什么</p>
<p begin="7211400000t" end="7228700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">到头来还不是只剩一片黄沙</p>
<p begin="7233000000t" end="7273500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">没错 如果只是镇压内乱也做得太过彻底了</p>
<p begin="7327100000t" end="7352900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">久违了 玛斯坦少校</p>
<p begin="7361700000t" end="7375900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">您还记得我吗</p>
<p begin="7385000000t" end="7397700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">为什么会这样</p>
<p begin="7403700000t" end="7440100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">她也有了这种杀人者的眼神…</p>
<p begin="7548900000t" end="7565400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">请你告诉我 少校</p>
<p begin="7573700000t" end="7616600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">本应守护国民的军人 为何会去杀害国民？</p>
<p begin="7630000000t" end="7682900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">本应带来幸福的炼金术 为何会用于杀戮？</p>
<p begin="7694900000t" end="7729400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">因为这就是国家炼金术师的工作</p>
<p begin="7735300000t" end="7777300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">为何本应守护国民的军人 会去杀害国民呢？</p>
<p begin="7780800000t" end="7810100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">因为这就是士兵的任务</p>
<p begin="7816300000t" end="7829500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">难道不是吗</p>
<p begin="7837800000t" end="7868300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">你是想说这样的惨状是理所当然的吗</p>
<p begin="7874200000t" end="7902500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">也是呢 比如说吧</p>
<p begin="7906900000t" end="7960100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">小姐你的表情在说「我是逼不得已的」对吧</p>
<p begin="7973000000t" end="7990000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">你敢肯定你在打倒对手的时候</p>
<p begin="7991800000t" end="8021100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">没有类似于「打中了！很好！」这种为自己的本领而自豪</p>
<p begin="8024800000t" end="8077200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">感觉到工作上的成就感的瞬间吗？</p>
<p begin="8082200000t" end="8095300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">狙击手小姐？</p>
<p begin="8102700000t" end="8114400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">不要再说了！</p>
<p begin="8122900000t" end="8162900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">就我来说 我反倒觉得你们更不可理解</p>
<p begin="8165600000t" end="8196500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">战场本来就是杀死敌人的地方</p>
<p begin="8213600000t" end="8245800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">你没有那种觉悟就敢穿起这身军装吗？</p>
<p begin="8265300000t" end="8294200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">不要对死亡视而不见 正视前方</p>
<p begin="8300900000t" end="8343100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">直面你所杀的那些人的身影</p>
<p begin="8351400000t" end="8395900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">然后永远铭记 敌人也不会忘记你的</p>
<p begin="8427100000t" end="8450700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">哎呀 到时间了</p>
<p begin="8454200000t" end="8469800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">得去工作了</p>
<p begin="8483700000t" end="8496300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我也得走了</p>
<p begin="8502300000t" end="8514900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">再见了 罗伊</p>
<p begin="8516900000t" end="8526500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">修兹</p>
<p begin="8538400000t" end="8551800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">为何你要战斗？</p>
<p begin="8576000000t" end="8619700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">很简单 我不想死 仅此而已</p>
<p begin="8627700000t" end="8647400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">理由总是很单纯的</p>
<p begin="8726300000t" end="8758300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">那么这场战争的理由到底是什么</p>
<p begin="8773600000t" end="8803200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">理由…是有的</p>
<p begin="8808300000t" end="8824800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">非常可怕的理由</p>
<p begin="9166400000t" end="9201800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">你是说用我们的血来制造贤者之石吗！</p>
<p begin="9207200000t" end="9222200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">那块石头哪去了？</p>
<p begin="9229800000t" end="9256700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">在乔尔夫·J·金布利少校</p>
<p begin="9262100000t" end="9287400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">红莲之炼金术师手中</p>
<p begin="9297900000t" end="9339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">是个束着黑色长发 有着冷酷眼神的男人吗</p>
<p begin="9365100000t" end="9376000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">大哥…</p>
<p begin="9397900000t" end="9408300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">接着说！</p>
<p begin="9411900000t" end="9456600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">局…局势只因为那一块石头而改变了</p>
<p begin="9481600000t" end="9507700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">啊 真是悦耳</p>
<p begin="9514600000t" end="9553600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">响彻身体内部的悦耳声音啊</p>
<p begin="9558400000t" end="9601600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">骨髓在悲伤地舞动 鼓膜因快乐而震颤</p>
<p begin="9604800000t" end="9666000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">这都是只有在这块与死常伴的土地上才能感觉到的喜悦</p>
<p begin="9684200000t" end="9710400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">这份工作还真是充实啊</p>
<p begin="9787100000t" end="9844000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">太悦耳了！太美妙了！贤者之石！</p>
<p begin="9889000000t" end="9924500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">歼灭的完成也只是时间问题而已了</p>
<p begin="9941800000t" end="9953300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">就在这时</p>
<p begin="9961000000t" end="10002900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">伊修瓦拉教的大僧正罗古·罗乌为了同胞</p>
<p begin="10008800000t" end="10027100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">站到了大总统的面前</p>
<p begin="10039800000t" end="10073300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">哦 你想以你一人之性命</p>
<p begin="10073900000t" end="10105600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">来拯救剩下的几万伊修瓦尔人？</p>
<p begin="10108800000t" end="10128100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">正是 我…</p>
<p begin="10128400000t" end="10141600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">少自以为是了</p>
<p begin="10150000000t" end="10202800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">你想说你一人的生命与剩下的数万生命等同？</p>
<p begin="10214200000t" end="10234200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">要有自知之明 人类</p>
<p begin="10242500000t" end="10279500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">一个人的生命只有他一人份的价值</p>
<p begin="10281190000t" end="10306500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">既不会多也不会少</p>
<p begin="10310990000t" end="10339200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">交易无效 歼灭也不会停止</p>
<p begin="10339600000t" end="10353590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">你这没人性的怪物！</p>
<p begin="10354300000t" end="10371900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">一定会遭到神罚的！</p>
<p begin="10373590000t" end="10406090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">你说神？那还真不可思议</p>
<p begin="10411700000t" end="10451600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">为什么现在还不来惩罚我呢？</p>
<p begin="10461190000t" end="10471500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">还要我杀几个…</p>
<p begin="10471700000t" end="10509200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">不 几千个伊修瓦尔人 神罚才会降临呢？</p>
<p begin="10511700000t" end="10521700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">混蛋</p>
<p begin="10528200000t" end="10590100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">所谓的神 只不过是由人所创造的人造产物</p>
<p begin="10597300000t" end="10619700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">想惩罚我的话</p>
<p begin="10624300000t" end="10668300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">就别依靠神 而是靠自己来挑战我吧 人类</p>
<p begin="10725800000t" end="10795000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">最后 战斗结束了 我们也终于能够回到故乡</p>
<p begin="10808200000t" end="10846800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">结果 我们军队只不过相当于炮灰而已</p>
<p begin="10849800000t" end="10892200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">是啊 终于知道个人的力量有多么有限了</p>
<p begin="10899800000t" end="10930500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">那么 我只要是能守住的东西…</p>
<p begin="10939000000t" end="10951000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">哪怕一点点也好</p>
<p begin="10956900000t" end="10973000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">要守住我最重要的东西</p>
<p begin="10983500000t" end="11012800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">下层的人就要守护更下层的人</p>
<p begin="11021200000t" end="11056700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">渺小的人类只能做到这样的事情了</p>
<p begin="11243500000t" end="11265800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">在伊修瓦尔有了那样的回忆</p>
<p begin="11270100000t" end="11289700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">你也还要选择这条道路吗</p>
<p begin="11295800000t" end="11304200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">是的</p>
<p begin="11314000000t" end="11330900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">如果真如炼金术所说的</p>
<p begin="11335400000t" end="11357800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">等价交换才是世界的真理</p>
<p begin="11364600000t" end="11404400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">那么 为了新生的世代能够享受幸福</p>
<p begin="11407900000t" end="11457000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">作为代价 我们要背负尸之山 趟过血之河</p>
<p begin="11491600000t" end="11520500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">我任命你为我的辅佐官</p>
<p begin="11529100000t" end="11551900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">我想让你来守护我的背后</p>
<p begin="11573900000t" end="11583400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">能明白吗？</p>
<p begin="11587200000t" end="11605800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">将背后交给你</p>
<p begin="11611200000t" end="11633600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">也意味着你随时可以在背后给我一枪</p>
<p begin="11641500000t" end="11660000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">如果我走错路的话</p>
<p begin="11663200000t" end="11675900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">就由你亲手杀了我</p>
<p begin="11684800000t" end="11699900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">你有这个资格</p>
<p begin="11713300000t" end="11725500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">你会跟着我吗？</p>
<p begin="11739200000t" end="11751500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">明白了</p>
<p begin="11758400000t" end="11781900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">如你所愿 至死相随</p>
<p begin="11834600000t" end="11858200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">但是哪怕上校站到军人的顶点</p>
<p begin="11861200000t" end="11892400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">这个国家也依然是一个军事国家啊</p>
<p begin="11897500000t" end="11907400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">是啊</p>
<p begin="11911400000t" end="11960000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">现在除非将成为军队傀儡的议会打回原形</p>
<p begin="11963000000t" end="11980000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">重新变为民主制</p>
<p begin="11987200000t" end="12017100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">将军事国家时代的脓血全部挤出</p>
<p begin="12021700000t" end="12039500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">否则这个国家就不会有什么改变</p>
<p begin="12043200000t" end="12053300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">脓血？</p>
<p begin="12062600000t" end="12123900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">比如说 制裁伊修瓦尔歼灭战的战争罪犯</p>
<p begin="12138000000t" end="12197200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">没错 乱世英雄放在和平时代就只是刽子手</p>
<p begin="12198500000t" end="12222900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">上校知道这点还要往上爬吗？</p>
<p begin="12227000000t" end="12246900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">这不是自取灭亡吗？</p>
<p begin="12264500000t" end="12305600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">在背后操控内乱的是人造人吧</p>
<p begin="12311000000t" end="12359400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">就算原因是人造人 实行的却是我们</p>
<p begin="12376100000t" end="12426200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">不可无视死亡 不可忘记被我们所杀的人</p>
<p begin="12430800000t" end="12484400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">因为 对方也绝对不会忘记是我们杀了他们</p>
<p begin="12499400000t" end="12510600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">但是…</p>
<p begin="12525500000t" end="12563800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">在担心我们之前 你还有事情要做吧</p>
<p begin="12570200000t" end="12606700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">不管阿尔冯斯还是你 都要恢复自己的身体</p>
<p begin="12614700000t" end="12651300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">有很多人都在等着那一天的到来呢</p>
<p begin="12679300000t" end="12707400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">嗯 绝对会恢复的</p>
<p begin="12712300000t" end="12723800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">我和阿尔冯斯都是</p>
<p begin="12743700000t" end="12768800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">诺克斯医生 打扰你了</p>
<p begin="12771400000t" end="12790700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">那个…铠甲先生</p>
<p begin="12793300000t" end="12801100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">嗯？</p>
<p begin="12804000000t" end="12840800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">你帮了我很多忙 真是谢谢你了</p>
<p begin="12844100000t" end="12873000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">不是铠甲 我叫阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克</p>
<p begin="12876800000t" end="12890100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">艾尔利克？</p>
<p begin="12893700000t" end="12917600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">你听说过爱德华·艾尔利克吧</p>
<p begin="12920200000t" end="12934600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">小个子的炼金术师</p>
<p begin="12939800000t" end="12961200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">我是他的弟弟</p>
<p begin="12965500000t" end="12990100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">因为一些原因才会变成这副身体的</p>
<p begin="12998300000t" end="13039600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">是他的弟弟？也就是说和他一样吗？</p>
<p begin="13039900000t" end="13050200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">太没礼貌了！</p>
<p begin="13051300000t" end="13083300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">我当然比我哥哥要高了！</p>
<p begin="13085800000t" end="13123300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">脸也没绷得那么紧 打架也比我哥哥要强！</p>
<p begin="13125100000t" end="13152200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">但是可没他粗暴 我是个绅士！</p>
<p begin="13170600000t" end="13192800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">阿尔冯斯大人！</p>
<p begin="13203200000t" end="13230100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">希望您的身体能早点恢复</p>
<p begin="13237400000t" end="13263700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">嗯 是啊</p>
<p begin="14179700000t" end="14210100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">马尔科医生 吃饭了</p>
<p begin="14223900000t" end="14252500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">咦？真安静啊</p>
<p begin="14257200000t" end="14290600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">难道又想起伊修瓦尔的事情而哭鼻子吗？</p>
<p begin="14312000000t" end="14350900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">（复仇）</p>
<p begin="14385800000t" end="14412100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">白色的恶魔被释放出来</p>
